" Work uses 3 spaces per tab, so respect that when editing a file in a
" subdirectory of 'Code/' via scp://.
autocmd! BufNewFile,BufRead scp://com/Code/* Tab 3

" Work around https://github.com/vim/vim/issues/2329 to allow writing netrw
" buffers.
autocmd! BufRead,BufWritePost scp://* :set buftype=acwrite
